HEADWORD: Banshie
<hw>Ban"shie</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> }</mhw>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gael. <ets>bean-shith</ets> fairy; Gael. & Ir.
<ets>bean</ets> woman + Gael. <ets>sith</ets> fairy.]</ety> <fld>(Celtic
Folklore)</fld> <def>A supernatural being supposed to warn a family of
